{"tid":1511223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［過時新聞，勿再推］美國會修法：限香港2020年真普選","createTime":"2019-08-27T12:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:18:07.000Z","uid":206523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7408d307ee26367e8286fff5eb6f3e2c667aec","tid":1511223,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"會員：王騎（#54373）<br />\n誤傳以下於6月早已發佈的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過時新聞</span></strong>：<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">美國國會眾議院議長裴洛西日前指出，如果香港就是中國，那麼香港不能享有獨立關稅區的優惠。（路透）<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕港人「反送中」催化美國國會跨黨派議員提出《2019年香港人權與民主法案》草案。雖然該法案曾在2017年時提出，不過，在今年修訂的版本中明訂，支持香港自由和公平地提名和選舉香港特首，並為「香港立法會舉行公開和直接選舉」設下了2020年的時限，否則將取消香港「獨立關稅區」特殊優惠......</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<em>資料來源：<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2833406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2833406&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=9cdbb0cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2833406&h=bcd89720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2833406</a><br />\n自由時報（2019-<span style=\"color: red;\">06-25</span> 20:51）<br />\n</em><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請各位瘋傳任何資訊之前，<br />\n留意其發佈時間、真確性，<br />\n以免因虛假／過時消息而錯判形勢。<br />\n記住：呢盤棋，一子錯，＿＿＿＿＿</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"903fe64b1788039d51f4dc5ce3b7d039c5c603b9","tid":1511223,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:52:44.000Z","msg":"自推十次 1/10"},{"pid":"bfd162cd31275fd315ee90502dc91d6585128f62","tid":1511223,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下